	<h1 class="title">纽森说，Apple Watch会是另一个iPhone，虽然数字不是这样说的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3603/small/3603.png?1414588369" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王杰夫 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-06 13:45:48 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17210/medium/17210.jpg?1446786933" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


